Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:34.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ばれなきゃいいと思ってんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did ya think it was all good as\Nlong as ya didn't get caught?! Well?!
