Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:28.77,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どさちゅ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now self-destruct, Yozora!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:30.48,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そこで自爆よ　夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:31.73,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,できるか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Like that's possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, you should be able to do that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:34.92,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ったく　自爆くらいできるようにしときなさいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika will fix up the explosion with CG.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:37.81,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,爆発もＣＧ処理しちゃいますね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:45.55,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,僕達の友情は地球さえも凌駕するだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Our friendship shall outshine planet Earth!\N- Planet Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:48.62,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あ　われらが全知全能たる女神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let us give thanks for the mercy...\N- Let us give thanks... whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...of the all-knowing, all-powerful\Ngoddess Kasi Vazwakii Swena!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:52.48,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,カスィ・ウァズァキィ・スェナ様の慈悲に感謝を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! This is love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:55.56,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなのだ　これが愛なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.53,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,意味わからない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,High school, friendship,\Nsinging, magic, superpowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:03.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,学園　友情　歌　魔法　超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,intergalactic samurai robot wars,\Nmale-male love scenes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:09.12,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,侍　ロボット　宇宙戦争　男同士のラブシーン
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Then I'll fly and my wings will float on\Nthe wind... can you make them sparkle?\N- Who knew she'd really\Nthrow all that in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:12.64,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に全部打ち込んでくるとはな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Then I'll fly and my wings will float on\Nthe wind... can you make them sparkle?\N- But hey, I guess it's got a\Nmore indie-film feel this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:17.36,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でもまあ　これはこれで自主映画っぽいか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Understood!\N- But hey, I guess it's got a\Nmore indie-film feel this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika feels bad for needing\Nyour help, Kodaka-sempai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:27.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すいません　小鷹先輩　手伝ってもらっちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:29.00,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,気にすんな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, walking\Nthe hallways all alone with Rika...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:33.20,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そういえ　理科と二人で廊下歩くのって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Walking the hallways all alone\Ntogether is a first, huh Sempai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:39.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こうして小鷹先輩と二人で廊下を歩くのって初めてですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:40.26,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだっけか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:41.41,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:42.62,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おんって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "hmm"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.22,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いらしゃいませ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:51.94,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そういえ　この部屋に入るってお前と初めて会った時以来だな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I haven't\Nbeen in this room since we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a while ago, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:54.28,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あれからずいぶん経ったよな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It was 122 days ago, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:55.92,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.28,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今日で122日になります
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been counting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:00.13,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,わざわざ数えてたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Rika just remembers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:02.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いいえ　覚えていただけです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To be precise, it's been 122 days,\N8 hours, and 37 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:09.42,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,正確には122日と8時間37分ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.75,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Sect {\fnArial Narrow}Σ{\fnJesaya Free}"\N"{\s1}Lab-Storage-Room{\s0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sect Sigma"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.87,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,セクトΣ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please pretend you didn't see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:18.15,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そこはスルーでお願いします
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:22.74,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すげえな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For a while, Rika even had fingerprint\Nand voice recognition on the lock
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:27.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一時期は秘密基地っぽく　指紋や声紋認証つけたこともあるんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to make it like a secret base!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You really do like this anime-type stuff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:30.81,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前ってこういうアニメみたいなの好きだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You've even got cosplay costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:32.66,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,コスプレー衣装も持ってるし
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.64,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうせ子供っぽいですよだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, fine, call Rika childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:45.71,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すげえな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can set the equipment down anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:48.65,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,機材はその辺に置いといてください
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sempai, you're the first person\NRika has ever let into this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:55.78,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この部屋にほかの人を入れるのは先輩が初めてです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:07:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"Huh"?! Please, try to be a little more moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:07:00.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ええって　もうちょっと感激してくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl is asking a boy into\Nher room for the first time, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:04.20,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,女の子が初めて部屋に男の人を招いたんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't convince me\Nthis place is a girl's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:08.11,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この部屋　女の子の部屋だと思いつうのは無茶だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good luck with the equipment checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:11.73,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃ　機材のチェック頑張ってくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:13.37,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,待ってください
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika's added some effects\Nto the scenes we've filmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:17.10,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,撮影済みのシーンにエフェクトをつけたので
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind taking a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.30,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,見てくれませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ No going back now! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:32.35,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あと戻り…できない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:36.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何　この力は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this power coming from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:37.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:43.15,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なかなかやるな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:54.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前凄いな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, don't just come out and say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:58.23,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう　そんなにストレートに言わないでくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But this really is amazing...\Nand wasn't it a lot of work?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:00.82,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だって　これ本当にすげえし
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:02.77,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,大変だったんじゃないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Rika did work pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:06.93,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　それなりに苦労しました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I feel bad that you're\Nhaving to shoulder all the burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:10.73,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そっか　お前にばっかり負担かけて悪いな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine! It's a lot of work,\Nbut it's certainly not a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:14.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いえいえ　確かに大変ですけど　負担なんかじゃないです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika has worked on a lot\Nof games and movies before,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:19.90,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ゲームや映画の仕事をしたことは何度もありますが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is her first time making\Nsomething with people her own age...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:24.24,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,同年代の人達と一緒に何かを作るのは初めてで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika's having a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:26.45,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,理科はとても楽しいです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:33.24,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\fscx80\pos(508,212)}Photos:\NFilm Backgrounds
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:33.24,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\fscx80\pos(662,344)}Photos:\NGame Backgrounds
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:33.24,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\fscx80\pos(820,476)}Photos:\NNeighbors Club Members
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Photos of the Neighbors Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.03,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,隣人部写真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:35.43,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\bord4\an8\pos(1080,468)}Photos:\NNeighbors Club Members
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:35.22,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これですか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.67,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,失礼ながら隠し撮りをさせていただきました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:37.57,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\be5\pos(576,336)}Photos:\NNeighbors Club Members
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika knows it was rude,\Nbut she took some secret photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.22,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この変態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:42.00,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,誤解しないでくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what {\i1}is{\i} this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:43.61,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃ何なんだ　これは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember how we all played\Nthat {\i1}Romancing sAgA{\i} game together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:48.34,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,前に皆で「ロマンシング佐賀」ってゲームをやったじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the reference materials\NRika got to make all your CG models.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:53.91,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの時　皆さんのＣＧモデル作成のために作った資料はこれです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:09:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She prepared that carefully\Njust to play the game with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:58.40,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつ　皆であのゲームをやるために
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:00.50,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなに入念に準備してたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, you found out.\NNow Rika feels a little embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:06.47,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ばれちゃいました　何か恥ずかしいですね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.76,0:09:08.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:10.77,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうかしましたか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no... Okay, well, I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:14.58,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　それじゃ俺もう帰るな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:17.13,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　お疲れ様でした
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Rika had a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:31.45,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですか　理科は楽しかったですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time Rika played\Na video game with other people,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:34.79,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,皆でゲームをやるというのは初めてでしたが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:36.88,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,とても楽しかったです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember getting lost\Nin her smile then, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:44.02,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの時もこいつの笑顔に見惚れたっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of all the Neighbors Club members,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:53.38,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺達隣人部の中で 一番真面目に友達を作ろうとしてるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,she might be the one\Ntrying hardest to make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:55.47,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつなのかもしれないな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:57.44,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Sect {\fnArial Narrow}Σ{\fnJesaya Free}"\N"{\s1}Lab-Storage-Room{\s0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.15,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"St. Chronica's Academy Middle School"\N\N"School Festival"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:06.98,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,保護者の方　こちらでどうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Parents and guardians this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing a maid café!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:09.58,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,メイド喫茶やってます
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:12.56,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord4\be4\pos(766,92)}Crêpes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:14.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すげえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Big Brother, is this an outdoor party?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:17.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なあなあお兄ちゃん　これお祭り
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:19.42,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　お祭りだな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so weird for a school\Nto be doing an outdoor party!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:22.52,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,学校なのにお祭りやっとるげ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the first time you've ever\Nbeen to a school festival, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:25.98,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,マリアは学園祭初めてなのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! See, when I was in school,\NI didn't do anything but study!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:29.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私の通ってた学校てはな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:31.83,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私は勉強しかやったことないな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:33.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dadadadada off we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:35.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,出発
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, Class 2-2...\NThere it is. The AV room, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:38.74,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,2年2組は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:40.99,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あった　視聴覚室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:43.86,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\bord4\be4\pos(326,152)\frz24.7}Screening Schedule - AV Room
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're starting at 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:43.64,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,10時から上映らしい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap, we only have five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:46.71,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,って　あと5分しかねえじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sena, where's the AV room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:48.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,星奈　視聴覚室ってどこだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:50.32,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何であたしに聞くのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:52.74,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前二年前まで通ってたんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You went to school here just two years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.36,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,通ってないわよ　中等部なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:56.84,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:11:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. I went to a public\Nmiddle school near my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:11:00.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,わたし中学は近所の公立だったから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, you\Ndid take the entrance exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:03.39,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そういえば貴様　普通に入試を受けていたな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So you weren't grandfathered\Nin from this middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:05.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,エスカレーター組ではなかったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it matter?\NCome on, let's find the AV room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:07.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことどうでもいいのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:09.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,早く視聴覚室探すわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:12.22,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"AV Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We will now screen a film by class 2-2.\NPlease be quiet during the screening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:15.49,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ただいまより　2年2組による映画の上映を始めます
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:19.41,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,上映中はくれぐれもお静かにお願いします
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, we made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:21.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何とか間に合った
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, please enjoy Kobato-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:26.80,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それでは小鳩様の姿をじっくりとご堪能ください
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kobato-{\i1}sama{\i0}"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:28.57,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩様
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.42,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Somewhere far away"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.84,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"in an old castle deep in the forest"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:44.35,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"there lived a beautiful princess."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:46.72,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Her name was"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:50.89,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Princess Kobato"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:52.49,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そのままかよッ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,At least rename her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:57.26,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"O beautiful Princess Kobato,\Nwill you marry me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:00.50,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"No, marry {\i1}me{\i0}!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:05.17,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Me! Me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:13.75,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Very well, I shall marry whoever brings me\Nthe jewel of the dragon at the end of the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:16.21,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,モチーフは輝夜姫か
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaguya-{\i1}hime{\i} motif, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:34.73,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Farewell..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:41.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺達の映画負けてるな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Our movie isn't as good as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Bravo! Bravo, Kobato-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.23,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ブラボー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:52.00,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩ちゃん　ブラボー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautifully performed.\NLeave it to your honored sister, Aniki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.81,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,見事なお手前でした
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:59.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さすが兄貴の妹君です
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika loves cutting-edge SFX,\Nbut that retro feel was good, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:01.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,最新のSFXも萌えますけど
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.85,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あいうレトロな感じもいいですね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Let's take a lesson from\Nthis for the movie we're mak...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:07.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに私達の作る映画の参考にさせてもらお…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kobato-{\i1}chan{\i} was so {\i1}cute{\i0}!\NShe's seriously a princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:10.10,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩ちゃん可愛かったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:11.84,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩まじお姫様
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart is melting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:13.02,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,きゅんきゅんする
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, Kobato-{\i1}sama's{\i} the best!\NSeriously a goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:17.15,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱ小鳩様　最高っす
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.31,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まじ神っす
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The audience was\Nseriously eating out of her hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:21.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お客さん達マジ魅了されてたのよね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,More like, how amazing is it\Nthat our first showing was that full?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:23.92,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ていうか　初回であんないっぱいで凄くない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If we get popular, we\Nmight not have enough seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:26.53,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,評判になったら席足りなくなるかも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should've sold tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:29.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,チケット売ってもよかったんじゃないすかね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Kobato-{\i1}sama{\i} for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さすが小鳩様
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobato-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:35.90,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see! I missed you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:38.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩ちゃん　久しぶり凄い会いたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cute! You're seriously an angel!\NYou're seriously Princess Kobato!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:40.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩ちゃん 可愛い
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:41.35,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩ちゃん マジ天使
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:42.92,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩ちゃん マジ小鳩姫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kobato-{\i1}chan,{\i} I just\N{\i1}love{\i} you! Sniff sniff! Pant pant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.47,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ もう好き好き　小鳩ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:47.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,クンカクンカ　スーハー　スーハー
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Leggo, dummy! Why're ya here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:48.54,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,放せ　アホたれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:50.13,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何であんたがおるじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, I told ya not to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:52.84,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんちゃんも こんといてて言ったや
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, are you Kobato-{\i1}chan{\i0}'s\Nbig brother that we hear so much about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:54.17,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:57.34,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もうしかして噂の小鳩ちゃんのお兄さんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you think? Wasn't she seriously good?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:13:59.83,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうでした
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:01.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩ちゃんマジよかったでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she was great.\NThe movie was really impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:05.10,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　凄かった あんなの撮れるな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobato-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Your big brother said\Nyou were super-good in the movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:06.58,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:09.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お兄さんが小鳩ちゃんの映画超よかったって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was super-good for me, too,\NKobato-{\i1}chan{\i0}! You were superb!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:13.69,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私も超よかったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:15.51,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩ちゃん最高だったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:18.41,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,アホ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:20.81,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\be5\an8\pos(300,70)\c&H5123E9&\3c&HF7F4FF&}Princess Kobato
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry that Sena interrupted you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:24.85,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何か　つれが邪魔して悪かったな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen... Is Kobato...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:31.38,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのさ　もしかして小鳩って人気者なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...a popular girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, very!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:32.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃもう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately her fan base has surged\Nall over school, let alone our class!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:34.21,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うちのクラスはもちろん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:36.93,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,学校中で小鳩ちゃんファン急増中です
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.28,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなのか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:39.34,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we totally want to\Nbe friends with Kobato-{\i1}chan{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:44.81,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まああたしらはめちゃ小鳩ちゃんと仲良くしたいんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but sometimes it kinda seems\Nlike she might not like us too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:50.10,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩ちゃんはあたしらのこと そんなに好きじゃないっぽいかもしれないとこあって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:51.84,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなのか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We tell her we love her all the time,\Nbut it's like she doesn't take us seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:54.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,めっちゃ好き好き言ってるんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:56.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本気にしてくれないって言うか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,or like the closer we get\Nthe more she pulls away...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:59.67,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,押せば押すほど小鳩ちゃんのほうが退いちゃうっていうか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry! I'm not\Nbadmouthing her or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:02.18,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんかすいません
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:04.34,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今の別に悪口とかじゃないで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I love that adorable shyness, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:07.32,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうしゃいなとこもラブリーで好きなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:08.32,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't take people seriously,\Npulls away the closer they get...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:13.30,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本気にしない　押せば押すほど退いちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Like brother, like sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:16.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがは兄弟ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:18.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:25.28,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした　マリア
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:28.02,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか　楽しくないのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You have waited long for me, my brethren.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:43.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,待たせたな　我が眷属共
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The poopy vampire! The poopy vampire is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:45.37,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うんこ吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:47.23,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うんこ吸血鬼が来たぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta kill the vampire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:50.54,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼をぶっ殺すのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.67,0:15:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You would defy me?\NYou never learn, foolish minion of...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:54.85,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,仕送りもなく我に刃向かうというのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:57.72,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,愚かなる神の下…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why do ya keep comin' at\Nme outta nowhere, ya dummy?!\N- Poopy! Poopy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:02.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何であんたはそんないつもいきなり来るじゃ　アホタレ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Taste my true power, which bends\Neven the power of God to my will!\N- Poopy! Poopy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:06.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,神の力も取り込んだ 我が真の力を受けてみよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get out there and film the\Nscene with the major Kobato-{\i1}chan{\i} heroics!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:12.10,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃさっそく　小鳩ちゃんが大活躍するシーンを撮りに行くわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember Kobato having a scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:14.10,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩のシーンなんであったっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course she does!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:15.41,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり前じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All the scenes that you've done so\Nfar, we're redoing with Kobato-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:17.45,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これまで小鷹がやってたシーンね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:19.45,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ全部小鳩ちゃん取り直すから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was a stand-in?! First I've heard of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.30,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺代役だったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:22.61,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,初耳なんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the sun! It's in the\Nperfect place, so let's hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.63,0:16:25.73,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今ちょうど夕日がいい感じなんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:26.35,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,早く
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I guess we'd better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.52,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,仕方ない　行くか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you my dark powers\Nthat sold out the theater, poopy nun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:33.58,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,マイン御礼を成しとけた我が闇の魔力を見せてやろう　うんこ聖女め
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll slaughter you with my sacred performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:38.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私の神聖な演技がお前をぶっ殺してやるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kobato-{\i1}chan{\i0}, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:41.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,待って小鳩ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Kodaka, get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:51.41,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら 小鷹　さっさと行くわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:52.99,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はい はい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a beautiful day without a cloud in\Nthe sky: the perfect day for a sports festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:02.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本日は雲一つもない秋晴れで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:04.74,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,絶好の体育祭日和となりました
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've all practiced hard for today,\Nso show us the fruits of your labor
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:09.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,生徒の皆さんはこの日のための練習の成果を存分に発揮し
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and give it your all until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:12.72,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,最後まで精一杯頑張ってください
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'd like to thank the parents\Nvery much for coming all this way.\N- Huh, our student council\Npresident is a girl. I never knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:18.92,夏雪日文旁白-ja,,0,0,0,,ご機嫌の皆様　本日は聖クロニカ学園に来てくれて 誠にありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:18.23,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うちの生徒会長って女子だったんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:19.68,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,初めて知った
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll cheer for us to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:23.44,夏雪日文旁白-ja,,0,0,0,,どうぞ最後までご声援賜りますよう　宜しくお願い致します
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've got nothing to\Ndo for a while. What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:27.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さって　しばらく暇だしどうっすかな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kodaka, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:33.15,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鷹か
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:36.54,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう帰ろうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:37.81,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はやえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have skipped after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:40.79,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱりさぼればよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still morning, and\NI've already seen something icky...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:42.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,朝から嫌な者見たし
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Something icky?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:44.49,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌な者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl who spoke at the opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:47.06,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,開会式で挨拶していたあの女だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Do you and the student\Ncouncil president not get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:50.00,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前生徒会長と仲悪いのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never even spoken.\NBut I hate her to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:52.00,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,話したこともない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だが死ぬほど嫌いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hidaka Hinata. Third year.\NOverwhelmingly popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:57.51,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,日高日向　三年生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:17:59.51,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,圧倒的な人望で
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is her {\i1}second{\i}\Nyear as student council president.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:02.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,去年から二年連続で生徒会長を勤めている
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She's good at all sports, and\Nall the teams ask her to fill in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:07.13,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,スポーツ万能で運動部からスケットとしてひっぱりだ子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She's extremely busy, and yet\NI hear she almost never refuses a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:08.63,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,多忙でありながら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:11.60,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,頼まれれば断ることはほとんどないと聞く
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The underclassmen idolize her, naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:14.24,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,当然後輩からも慕われている
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems like a really good person...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:16.64,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,めちゃくちゃいい人っぽいな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hidaka Hinata... she is a true real-lifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:20.10,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,日高日向　やつこそ真のリア充
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I've uncovered\Nhow tragically stupid Meat is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:23.99,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,肉が残念無双の馬鹿だと発覚した今となっては
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,she stands alone at the\Nsatisfying-real-life summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:26.53,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,唯一無二のリア充界の頂点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,One might even rightly call her King Real.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:30.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いわば　リア王の名に相応しいと言えるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"King Real"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:31.70,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,リア王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,One of Shakespeare's great tragic plays
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:33.93,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,シェイクスビア四大悲劇の一つだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is the story of the elderly king\NLear causing numerous tragedies
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:36.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,年老いた王リアは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:40.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,戦の悲劇を引き起こした末に憐れな最後遂げる物語で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and ultimately dying a pathetic death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost the entire cast dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:43.02,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,登場人物大体皆死ぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty sinister nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:44.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,陰湿なネーミングですね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It expresses my wish that her life ends badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:49.65,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やつの人生がバッドエンドになるようにという願えをこめていた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to feel\Nsick just talking about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:53.90,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やつのこと話しだけで気分が悪くなってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go rest in the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:56.07,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,とりあえず保健室で休む
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:18:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How much do you hate real-lifers, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:59.23,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前どんだけ嫌いだよ　リア充
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:04.46,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,理科
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:06.87,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何やってんだ　あいつ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sempai! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:12.73,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何でこんな所に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:16.11,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃこっちのせりふだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika wanted to feel the wind for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:18.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと風に当たりたくなりまして
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're dressed like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:21.80,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何て格好してるんだ　お前は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika decided to wear a gym uniform\Nfor the occasion. How does it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:24.38,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかくなので　体操着を着てみました
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:25.66,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,似合いますか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not just participate while you're at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:28.66,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ついでに参加すりゃいいんじゃないか　体育祭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Rika still has work to do.\NNot that she would join if she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:30.66,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いいえ　まだ作業があるので
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:32.72,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　なくても出ませんけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you pull an all-nighter last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.99,0:19:35.37,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前　もしかして昨日寝てないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, you caught on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:37.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ばれましたか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps Rika should have worn her glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:40.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱりだてめがねでもかけておけばよかったですね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I, um... well... Thanks for\Nworking so hard for us, Rika.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:43.50,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんつうか　そのう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:46.26,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張ってくれてありがとうな　理科
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,For goodness's sake! Hasn't Rika told\Nyou to stop blindsiding her like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:51.23,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　まったくも
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:55.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうやってたまに不用意で直球投げてくるのをやめてて言ったじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:20:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rika thinks the race is about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.79,0:19:59.94,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら　駆けっ子が始まるみたいですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's Sena-{\i1}sempai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:04.72,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,星奈先輩ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, that's a lot of jiggling!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:07.63,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ばいんばいん揺れてますね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:11.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どこ見てるんだ　お前は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Altogether Sena-{\i1}sempai{\i}\Nreally is impressive, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:16.66,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱりなんだかんだで凄いですね　星奈先輩は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:17.64,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, what do you think of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:21.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちなみに　星奈先輩のことどう思ってるんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anything!\NShe's just a fellow club member.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:26.09,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,別にどうって　ただの部活仲間だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she's your betrothed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:27.47,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いいなずけなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all over and done with!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.37,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それはもう終わった話だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm. Rika doesn't think\NSena-{\i1}sempai{\i} agrees with you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.38,0:20:35.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,星奈先輩にとってはそうでもないみたいですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:37.09,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always lonely, but you're\Nscared of open affection from others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:48.01,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,寂しがり屋のくせに他人に率直な好意を向けられるのが怖い
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You pretend not to notice.\NYou pretend not to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.36,0:20:49.79,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,気付かない振りをする
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:51.09,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,聞こえない振りをする
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You run. You make jokes.\NYou brush off. You reject.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:52.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:52.98,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,茶化す
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:53.95,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ごまかす
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:55.15,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,拒絶する
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:21:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You even lie to your own heart,\Nand tell it "They {\i1}don't{\i} like you."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:59.49,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自分は好かれてなどいないだと　自分の心にさえ嘘をつく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're talking about Kobato.\NYeah, she's always been scared of strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:01.84,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鳩のことか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:04.61,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつ昔から人見知りだったからな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"What did you say," my ass. Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:07.02,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,「何だって」じゃねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:08.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,馬鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika will keep playing the\Nsame character she's always played,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:11.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,先輩が望むなら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:14.62,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,理科はこれからもこれまでどおりのキャラクターを通しますけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,if that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kodaka-{\i1}sempai{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:17.71,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でもね　小鷹先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's about time\Nyou moved forward? After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:21.24,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もうそろそろ先に進んでもいいんじゃないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:22.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:23.03,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:31.52,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はもう行くから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we're already...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:38.49,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だって　理科達はもう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.05,0:21:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already your...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:42.22,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,理科達はもう…じゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:46.72,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.24,0:22:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I knew which\Nword the wind had swallowed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.30,0:22:00.65,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,風に消えた言葉は何だったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:03.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は本当は知っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I'd realized it long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.60,0:22:08.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本当はもう　とっくに気付いていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.06,0:22:33.45,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,光ったはずの星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.10,0:22:33.44,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hikatta hazu no ano hoshi{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.44,0:22:38.94,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mayotta kumo ga jama shite mienaku naru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:36.67,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,迷った雲が邪魔して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:38.77,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,見えなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.94,0:22:42.44,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nani wo shinjitara ii?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.16,0:22:42.06,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何を信じたらいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:46.28,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fuantei sugiru sekai de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.22,0:22:46.48,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,不安定すぎる世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:52.12,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sodatta takaramono kowashikaketeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:51.58,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,育った宝物壊しかけてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.12,0:22:56.23,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nakusu no ga kowakute{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.22,0:22:55.15,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なくすのが怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:22:59.50,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fujouri datte tameiki tsuki{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.26,0:22:57.97,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,不条理だって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:22:59.29,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ため息つき
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:02.64,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうにかどうで足掻いてた日々
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:02.77,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Torikago de agaiteta hibi{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:08.94,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Onaji sora wo miageteta n da bokura wa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.89,0:23:07.05,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,同じ空を見上げてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.33,0:23:08.98,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.94,0:23:15.28,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kimi no te wo nigitta{\i}\N{\i1}toki nigirikaeshite kureta ne{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.00,0:23:12.30,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,君の手を握った時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:15.49,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,握り返してくれたね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.28,0:23:21.82,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsunagatta kono te wa{\i}\N{\i1}donna hane yori tsuyoi n da{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.53,0:23:18.63,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,繋がったこの手は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.74,0:23:22.10,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな羽より強いんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.82,0:23:28.36,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsubasa nante nakutatte motto takaku toberu kara{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.12,0:23:25.25,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,翼だってなくったって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.28,0:23:28.54,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと高く飛べるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.36,0:23:31.76,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kitto ima nara daijoubu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.56,0:23:31.78,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,きっと今なら大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.76,0:23:37.50,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oozora kagayaku hoshi wo tsukamou{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.81,0:23:36.90,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,大空輝く星を掴もう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.01,0:23:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Be My Friend! Yeah, you played dumb! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.04,0:23:42.00,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,Be my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.00,0:23:44.31,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,知らない振りしたって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.57,0:23:45.66,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.71,0:23:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Be My Side! But I saw right through you! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.85,0:23:46.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,Be my side
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.76,0:23:49.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,全部気付いてたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.11,0:23:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.76,0:23:50.88,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.48,0:23:52.88,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,のりのりですね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.48,0:23:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure into this. You just\Nruined the somber mood of the episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.88,0:23:54.74,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本編の余韻ぶっち壊しですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.62,0:23:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I figured I'd at least\Ngive the preview some spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:57.47,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,予告くらいは盛り上げてこうと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.39,0:23:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.57,0:23:58.56,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.62,0:24:09.86,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\fscx90\fad(1000,0)\pos(640,420)}"{\c&H8728E4&}Dismay {\c&HFFFFFF&}of I, {\c&H10E5B0&}the {\c&H0BEAF8&}Chicken{\c&HFFFFFF&}"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.96,0:24:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: "Dismay of I, the Chicken."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.07,0:24:01.46,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,次回　「迷えるチキンな俺」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.39,0:24:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sempai! Please marry Rika!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.68,0:24:05.94,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,先輩　理科と結婚してください
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.70,0:24:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.30,0:24:06.88,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.90,0:24:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.34,0:24:08.06,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だって
